channel.description:
[center][url=http://runetrack.com/timezone_converter][img]http://runetrack.com/timezone_converter/1337148000/nsw/Dungeoneering.png[/img][/url] [url=http://sign.tip.it][img]http://sign.tip.it/g1/25/80/Fixed_Pouch.png[/img][/url][/center]
[b]My Information[/b] Username: Fixed Pouch. Requirements: Nothing. E-mail: Skyro@runedream.org Dungeoneering Level: 70. World: 88.
[b]Floors[/b] We'll be doing 20+ floors on large and we will be rushing c6's. Note: Anyone who wants to sui key, and dung can and will be much appreciated.
[b]Event[/b] Hey, I'm hosting a Dungeoneering event at the time set on the banner, when the timer is at 0 come to world 88 and add my username that's stated above. We will dungeoneer all night and try and get a lot of levels.
Please fill this out below so we can work out what floors we can do with you, and so we can contact each other in-game.
Note: I will smith any items for people if they want for a price, because I'm 99 smithing.
See you there.
[code] Username: Dungeoneering Level: Mining Level: Smithing Level:[/code]
